race.description: Phil Mclennan Earthmoving Masters Final F
race.comment: PARTY MODE (1) had second look this course and distance latest and improved on his time, finishing a 1.5 lengths second in 20.23. Expected to push the clock again here. CASH IN COLOUR (7) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind BRODIES TIGER (20.45) in a Mix 2/3. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Has performed well from this box with a win and four minor placings to his name from seven starts. Must be included in calculations. NITRO SLIM (2) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 20.13 beating PARTY MODE. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. One of the leading chances again. BRODIES TIGER (5) scored in impressive time last start. Right in the mix.

runners.name: Nitro Slim
